0:00:00.000,0:00:01.060
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:00:01.060,0:00:07.580
Zita rangu ndi Georgiana Saffa, ndakaberekerwa ku Sierra Leone, ndinogara ku UK.

0:00:07.580,0:00:10.860
Ndine makore makumi mashanu nemashanu.

0:00:10.860,0:00:13.320
Ndange ndichigara mu UK kwemakore 25.

0:00:13.320,0:00:16.360
Upenyu hwangu hwose mu UK hwakanga huzere nehurwere.

0:00:16.360,0:00:19.480
Handina kumbobvira ndave nenguva yakanakisisa mu UK.

0:00:19.480,0:00:25.080
Ndakatanga kushanda, ndakadzikama ndokutenga dzimba.

0:00:25.080,0:00:31.160
Ndine dzimba dzinenge nhatu mu London kuburikidza nebasa randakanga ndiri kuita - basa rakanaka chaizvo -

0:00:31.160,0:00:36.940
kubatsira vakadzi ve munharaunda avo vaiedza kugara munyika,

0:00:36.940,0:00:41.940
vachiedza kuenda kukoreji, kana kutanga ma bhizinesi avo kana kuwana basa.

0:00:41.940,0:00:46.600
Ndiro basa randakanga ndichiita - raida kushanda kwakanyanya zvikuru-ndichimhanya mhanya  -  kwavari.

0:00:46.600,0:00:49.860
Pane imwe nguva, vaideedza imba yangu kuti, Imba ye Social Service -magariro evanhu

0:00:49.860,0:00:54.660
nokuti pakarepo mumwe munhu anosvika, munhu wokutanga wavaizo fonera ndini.

0:00:54.660,0:00:56.860
... zvinetso zvepekugara, zvose.

0:00:56.860,0:00:59.420
Basa iri raifamba zvakanaka kwandiri mu London.

0:00:59.420,0:01:04.360
Upenyu hwangu hwaive hwakaisvonaka kwazvo; Ndakanga ndichityaira motokari yakanaka, motokari itsva.

0:01:04.360,0:01:09.040
Mu London, tinotyaira nekunyoresa; gore rimwe nerimwe, motokari inobuda -

0:01:09.040,0:01:11.640
iwe unoityaira uye vanhu vanoti une mari.

0:01:11.640,0:01:12.880
Ndakanga ndisina matambudziko.

0:01:12.880,0:01:16.300
Pane imwe nguva, hurumende yakandipa motokari kuti ndidhiraivhe.

0:01:16.300,0:01:18.380
Ndakanga ndine mukurumbira kwazvo mu London.

0:01:18.380,0:01:22.940
Ndakawana basa muhofisi ya MP.

0:01:22.940,0:01:30.220
Ndakava mukuru we kambeni ye nzvimbo ye Westminster yose - Kumaodzanyemba.

0:01:30.220,0:01:40.520
Ndaishanda muhofisi iyi iyo iri chikamu che Bato re Labour Party.

0:01:40.520,0:01:46.940
Pese apo sarudzo yaiuya, ndakanga ndiri mumwe wevashandi wemazuva ose aita basa iri.

0:01:46.940,0:01:50.080
Ndaienda kunzvimbo yekuvhotera, sechimwe chezvinhu zvandaifanira kuita.

0:01:50.080,0:02:00.260
Ndini apo pamufananidzo ndina MP - Karen Buck, mu Westminster City Council.

0:02:00.260,0:02:01.680
Ndiyo ofisi yandaimboshandira.

0:02:01.680,0:02:04.240
Aiva shamwari yangu yepedyo.

0:02:04.240,0:02:05.520
Uyu ndiye mutungamiri wedu.

0:02:05.520,0:02:13.680
Paakauya ku London, vakamuudza kuti ndaibatsira vakawanda veku Sierra Leone vaiva vapoteri.

0:02:13.680,0:02:17.600
Ini ndaive ndichivabatsira uye purezidhendi akafara nezvazvo.

0:02:17.600,0:02:21.740
Uyu ndiye mwanakomana wangu wokupedzisira - uyo vakatora kubva kwandiri pandakanga ndiri muchipatara.

0:02:21.740,0:02:23.860
Iye zvino, ane makore gumi nemanomwe.

0:02:23.860,0:02:32.060
Ava ndivo vanasikana vangu vaviri - anenge masvondo matatu apfuura vakandishanyira ku Ghana kekutanga.

0:02:32.060,0:02:35.420
Zvinhu zvose zvaifamba zvakanaka kwandiri.

0:02:35.420,0:02:42.320
Ipapo, ndakatanga kutemwa nemusoro usingapere.

0:02:42.320,0:02:49.960
Ndakaudza munun'una wangu mukoti pamusoro pezve kutema nemusoro kwangu ne kusakwanisa kurara.

0:02:49.960,0:02:56.480
Akapindura kuti zvaityisa uye kuti ndinofanira kuenda kuna chiremba wangu kuti ndiongororwe uropi.

0:02:56.480,0:03:01.740
Panguva iyoyo, ndakanga ndichiri kushanda asi maitiro angu muhofisi akanga akaipa

0:03:01.740,0:03:05.080
kusvika pekuti vakaisa makamera kuti vaone zvandaita muhofisi, pasina ruzivo rwangu.

0:03:05.080,0:03:10.320
Saka nguva yose, pandainge ndichirwisana nevamwe vangu, vakanga vachirekodha.

0:03:10.320,0:03:15.500
Rimwe zuva, maneja akandifonera ndokundiudza kuti aida kundiona muhofisi, kuti pane dambudziko.

0:03:15.500,0:03:17.480
Ndakati, "Zvakanaka", ndichauya.

0:03:17.480,0:03:23.620
Pandakazosvika ikoko, vakandiratidza zvakaitika kare zve maitiro angu echisimba.

0:03:23.620,0:03:27.700
Kunyange nzira yandaitaura nayo kune makasitoma pafoni yakanga yakarekondwa yose.

0:03:27.700,0:03:33.000
Vakandiudza kuti mamiriro angu aive akaoma zvikuru saka vakanga vasingachagoni kundipa basa.

0:03:33.000,0:03:34.900
Vakandiudza kuti ndiende kunotsvaka rubatsiro.

0:03:34.900,0:03:38.420
Pakarepo ndakaudza munini'na wangu, akati ini ndaifanira kuona chiremba wangu.

0:03:38.420,0:03:39.940
Ndakatumirwa kuti ndiitwe MRI scan.

0:03:39.940,0:03:47.140
Sikani yekutanga yakaitwa, ndakaudzwa kuti tsinga dzepakati pe huropi hwangu dzaive dzichizvimba.

0:03:47.140,0:03:50.140
Ndicho chikonzero nei ndakanga ndiine zvi bumbo zveropa mumaziso angu.

0:03:50.140,0:03:52.320
Handaikwanisa kurara zvakanaka.

0:03:52.320,0:03:54.500
Zvose zvinetso izvi zvaiuya.

0:03:54.500,0:03:57.300
Ndakaiswa pamushonga.

0:03:57.300,0:04:06.460
Pakutanga, waiva umwe chete asi ndakaguma ndavekutora marudzi gumi nemana emishonga.

0:04:06.460,0:04:11.800
Mimwe yacho yaive ye maitiro angu asi imwe yacho yakaita kuti ndive ne dambudziko reitsvo.

0:04:11.800,0:04:13.900
Asi ndinotenda Mwari nekuda kwa Jesu kuti zvaenda.

0:04:13.900,0:04:16.120
Matambudziko angu apera. Ndinotenda Mwari.

0:04:16.120,0:04:26.980
Aya magwaro akabva kuna chiremba - GP wangu ku London achitaura mishonga yandakanga ndichitora.

0:04:26.980,0:04:34.760
Ndakanga ndiine mishonga yemafungiro, yekurara, yeasima neye mhepo.

0:04:34.760,0:04:41.480
Ndakanga ndichibuda ropa nokuda kwemishonga yakawandisa mumuviri wangu.

0:04:41.480,0:04:43.220
Zvose izvo zvakaita kuti nditemwe nemusoro.

0:04:43.220,0:04:45.460
Ndakanga ndichipfuura nemumatambudziko akawanda.

0:04:45.460,0:04:52.320
Aya matambudziko akava rugwadzo rukuru kwandiri zvokuti vana vangu vakatorwa kubva kwandiri pakarepo.

0:04:52.320,0:05:01.140
Ndakanga ndisingafari kuti vana vangu vakabviswa kwandiri asi ivo vakanga vari vaduku uye vasinga kwanise kuudza hurumende kuti vaida mai vavo

0:05:01.140,0:05:03.760
kunze kwekuti une makore gumi nematanhatu kana gumi ne manomwe.

0:05:03.760,0:05:06.580
Kana uri mucheche vanongo kutorwa.

0:05:06.580,0:05:08.320
Vana vangu vakaiswa kunochengetedzwa vana.

0:05:08.320,0:05:10.780
Kuona vana vangu kwaiva dambudziko kwandiri.

0:05:10.780,0:05:14.680
Zvakatora chinguva kuti ndidzokere kuva ini zvakare.

0:05:14.680,0:05:21.960
Pandatanga kuona vana vangu vaitarisisa ini nevana vangu.

0:05:21.960,0:05:25.720
Vhidhiyo kamera yaive iri pandiri kuti vaone nzira yandaizvibata nayo.

0:05:25.720,0:05:33.880
Mushure meawa rimwe kana maviri, ndaizoudzwa kuti musangano nevana vangu wapera.

0:05:33.880,0:05:43.640
Panguva iyoyo, ndaizobata mimba nemhando dzakasiyana dzevarume vaizondishandisa.

0:05:43.640,0:05:51.840
Ndakabvisa pamuviri kasere uye vana vanomwe nana baba vakasiyana.

0:05:51.840,0:05:54.620
Vamwe vavo vakange vasingamboziva madzibaba avo.

0:05:54.620,0:05:57.120
Dzimwe nguva vaizondibvunza kuti baba vavo vaivepi ini ndaizopindura kuti ndakanga ndisingazivi -

0:05:57.120,0:06:01.080
panguva iyoyo, ndakanga ndiri pamishonga uye ndichirwara zvikuru.

0:06:01.080,0:06:07.820
Medhemu munoreva here kuti - nekuda kwedambudziko iri, maive nevana vanomwe kubva kuvarume vatanhatu vakasiyana?

0:06:07.820,0:06:08.640
Ehe.

0:06:08.640,0:06:12.240
Uye vazhinji vevana venyu havazivi kuti baba vavo ndiani?

0:06:12.240,0:06:13.560
Ichokwadi, hongu.

0:06:13.560,0:06:17.340
Kunyange ikozvino, handizivi chekuvataurira.

0:06:17.340,0:06:28.060
Zvose izvi zvakaita kuti ndirege kuchengetwa, kunyange nemhuri yangu, 15 vavo vandakaunza ku London.

0:06:28.060,0:06:30.060
Hapana mumwe wavo akauya kuzondibatsira.

0:06:30.060,0:06:31.540
Ndakanga ndakashairwa hanya kwazvo.

0:06:31.540,0:06:34.300
Hapana aive ne hanya ne zvehutano kana hurwere hwangu.

0:06:34.300,0:06:39.940
Vaive vachito ndiseka, vachitaura kuti ndakanga ndiri mukadzi anopenga - kurwara nepfungwa, kuti ndakange ndisisina basa.

0:06:39.940,0:06:42.960
Nemhaka yekurwara uku, ndakapa upenyu hwangu kuna Kristu.

0:06:42.960,0:06:44.920
Ndakaberekwa semu Chawa.

0:06:44.920,0:06:50.300
Zvakanaka. Ndine urombo, musati maenda mberi madhamu - imi mataura kuti nokuti mamiriro ezvinhu aive akanyanya kuoma,

0:06:50.300,0:06:53.840
hurumende yaifanira zvochokwadi kutora vana venyu kubva kwamuri.

0:06:53.840,0:06:59.840
Maitiro enyu aive akaita sei kumba zvakaita kuti hurumende iuye kuzotora vese vanomwe

0:06:59.840,0:07:03.660
vana kubva kwamuri, kuti vavaise kunochengetwa vana?

0:07:03.660,0:07:07.320
Chekutanga ndakanga ndisingagoni kuchengeta ini kana vana vangu.

0:07:07.320,0:07:09.940
Vakanga vasina kuitirwa hanya - vachienda kuchikoro netsvina.

0:07:09.940,0:07:13.520
Dzimwe nguva, vaisazoenda kuchikoro; mangwanani, ndaingopfiga musuo wangu

0:07:13.520,0:07:15.120
uye kuti, "Hakuna chikoro nhasi!"

0:07:15.120,0:07:19.760
Ve kuchikoro vakafonera avo vanoona nezve magariro evanhu vachivaudza kuti vana vangu vakanga vasinga one vana vangu kuchikoro.

0:07:19.760,0:07:26.460
Ve zve magariro evanhu vakapindira, vakauya kumba kwangu ndokutora vana vangu kubva kwandiri.

0:07:26.460,0:07:28.900
Ms Georgiana Saffa Uchapupu hwe Morning Water

0:07:28.900,0:07:31.540
Panguva iyoyo, ndaida kuzviuraya.

0:07:31.540,0:07:37.980
Ndakanga ndichigara pamuturikidzwa we chitatu asi vakandiisa muimba ye pasi pasi nekuda kuedza kuzviuraya kwangu.

0:07:37.980,0:07:39.920
Zvakanaka, imi mati makaedza kuzviuraya.

0:07:39.920,0:07:44.640
Imi makanyatsoedza sei kuita  izvi, nekuda kwe kurwara mupfungwa kwamaiva nako panguva iyoyo?

0:07:44.640,0:07:49.080
Ndakaedza kuzviuraya kashanu kana katanhatu.

0:07:49.080,0:07:55.240
Pavakazosvika pakuziva, vakandiisa pasi pasi uye vakandiisa pane Kutariswa Kwekuzviuraya.

0:07:55.240,0:08:01.560
Kunyangwe pandakanga ndiri muchimbudzi ne muchigezero,mumba, mangu, mumwe munhu aifanira kuva neni nguva dzose

0:08:01.560,0:08:07.560
kunditarisa, vachinyora pasi kuti ndanga ndichizvibata sei uye chii chakanga chichiitika muupenyu hwangu.

0:08:07.560,0:08:12.040
Pawakanga uri pamuturikidzwa wechitatu - zvaiva nekuti wakaedza kusvetuka here?

0:08:12.040,0:08:17.140
Hungu, ndakaedza kusvetuka kanenge ka5.

0:08:17.140,0:08:24.480
Mumwe wevanasikana vangu akandiona ndichizviita ndokuudza mapurisa kuti amai vake vaida kuzviuraya.

0:08:24.480,0:08:29.920
Ndinofunga kuti isu tose tinogona kunzwisisa kukura kwedambudziko rehanzvadzi yedu,

0:08:29.920,0:08:34.240
kusvika pamwero wekuti vafanirwa kuongororwa 24/7 nguva dzose.

0:08:34.240,0:08:36.360
Akaiswa pasi pe Kutariswa Kwe Kuzviuraya.

0:08:36.360,0:08:43.380
Mumwe munhu aifanira kuva naye nguva dzose nekuda kwekuoma kwemamiriro epfungwa dzake, izvozvo zvakamusundira

0:08:43.380,0:08:46.280
kuedza kuzviuraya kakawanda.

0:08:46.280,0:08:54.140
Izvo zvisati zvaitika iwe wataura kuti izvi zvakatungamirira varume vakawanda vakasiyana kuti vakushandise nekukubata chibharo.

0:08:54.140,0:08:55.340
Unorevei naizvozvo?

0:08:55.340,0:09:01.040
Iwe waisangana sei nevarume vakadaro uye vaikushandisa sei, mune dambudziko rako repfungwa?

0:09:01.040,0:09:05.360
Chekutanga ndiri mukadzi anozivikanwa kwazvo muLondon.

0:09:05.360,0:09:10.760
Ndaiva neshamwari dzevarume asi ndakanga ndisina ukama navo.

0:09:10.760,0:09:19.740
Apo vaiziva kuti ndairwara uye kuti ndaive ndisina simba, vamwe vavo vaiuya kwandiri se shamwari,

0:09:19.740,0:09:23.860
vachitaura kuti ivo chete ndivo vainzwisisa dambudziko rangu, kuti handifaniri kunetseka sezvavaizova neni

0:09:23.860,0:09:29.300
asi nekufamba kwenguva, apo ndaizovaudza kuti ndaive nepamuviri navo, vaibva vanyangadika.

0:09:29.300,0:09:33.460
Nenhumbu dzacho, hurumende yakati sezvo ini ndaisagona kuzvichengeta pachangu,

0:09:33.460,0:09:35.260
Ndakanga ndisingagoni kuchengeta vana vangu.

0:09:35.260,0:09:39.020
Saka, vamwe vevana vakatorwa kubva kwandiri panguva yandakanga ndiri muchipatara.

0:09:39.020,0:09:45.020
Zuva randaibata pamuviri, vaizondi chengetedza, vachindiendesa kuchipatara nekundiitira zvose.

0:09:45.020,0:09:49.180
Zuva rokuzvara rangu, handimbo mirira kurwadziwa; vaizoita oparesheni

0:09:49.180,0:09:53.280
nokuti vakanga vasingadi kuti ndirwadziwe vachityira kuti ndaigona kuuraya mwana wacho.

0:09:53.280,0:09:56.400
Vaizongo ndiopareta, votora mwana uye pakarepo,

0:09:56.400,0:09:59.700
Vabereki vaizochengeta mwana vainge varipo kuti vatore mwana kubva kwandiri.

0:09:59.700,0:10:01.260
Handina kumbo yamwisa zvachose.

0:10:01.260,0:10:06.020
Panguva yawakasununguka vana ava, vakatorwa nehurumende pakarepo?

0:10:06.020,0:10:08.980
Pakarepo, vaifanira kuenda.

0:10:08.980,0:10:13.600
Vamwe vavo handina kumbovaona kwe makore 10 kana 15

0:10:13.600,0:10:15.500
Vamwe vavo vane makore 22.

0:10:15.500,0:10:21.700
Iko zvino ndipo pavave kuuya muupenyu hwangu nenyasha dziri muhupenyu hwe mu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:10:21.700,0:10:25.960
Ndinokutendai, Jesu!

0:10:25.960,0:10:32.300
Kamwezve, tiri kungobvunza mubvunzo uyu kuti munhu wese anzwisise kuoma kwemamiriro acho ezvinhu.

0:10:32.300,0:10:39.100
Hanzvadzi yedu isati yauya pa SCOAN kuburikidza nenyasha dza Mwari, akanga abereka vana vakawanda

0:10:39.100,0:10:44.340
asi iye akanga asingakwanisi kugara navo seamai nekuda kwemamiriro ake epfungwa,

0:10:44.340,0:10:50.860
kunyange kusvika apo vamwe vevana vake vekupedzisira vakatorwa kubva kwaari mushure mekuberekwa, muchipatara

0:10:50.860,0:10:52.400
nekuiswa kune vano chengeta vana.

0:10:52.400,0:10:57.480
Vakarerwa vasingazive amai vavo nekuda kwekuoma kwemamiriro avo.

0:10:57.480,0:11:03.080
Saka madhamu, imi mati makaedza nenzira dzakawanda dzakasiyana-siyana kuti mugadzirise dambudziko iri,

0:11:03.080,0:11:05.000
musati masvika pa SCOAN.

0:11:05.000,0:11:12.260
Mungagone here kutaura zvakare dzimwe nzvimbo dzakasiyana-siyana dzamakaenda, muchiedza kubvisa dambudziko iri?

0:11:12.260,0:11:18.100
Nguva yokutanga pandakapinda muchechi, ndine shamwari, iye anobva ku Uganda - akauya kumba kwangu

0:11:18.100,0:11:22.360
uye akandiudza kuti ndaive munhu akanaka chaizvo asi kuti ndaifanira kumutevera kuchechi.

0:11:22.360,0:11:26.260
Mudzimai uyu akanditevera kwemwedzi inopfuura mitanhatu.

0:11:26.260,0:11:33.260
Rimwe zuva, amai vangu vaiva neni uye vakanditaurira kuti nditevere shamwari yangu kuchechi, kuti Jesu andiporese.

0:11:33.260,0:11:40.160
Pakarepo, ndakasimuka, ndaka chinja mbatya dzangu ndokutevera mukadzi iyeye kuchechi.

0:11:40.160,0:11:43.060
Paakaenda neni kuchechi, ndakapa upenyu hwangu kuna Kristu.

0:11:43.060,0:11:48.460
Ndakatanga kuenda kumachechi akasiyana, kurara muchechi, kunyange pasi.

0:11:48.460,0:11:50.060
Ndairara pasi muchechi.

0:11:50.060,0:11:55.140
Vanhu vaizondiseka, vachindinyomba vachiti, "Iwe hausati wamboona chinhu asi izvi hazvisi kuzoenda".

0:11:55.140,0:12:05.140
Ndakaenda kuMali, Senegal neGambia kunoita zvibayiro zvakasiyana.

0:12:05.140,0:12:11.760
Vanhu vaindiziva vaizopa mari vachindiudza kuti ndiende kunzvimbo dzakasiyana-siyana kuti ndinotsvaka kuporeswa.

0:12:11.760,0:12:14.820
Iwe wati pawakaenda kunyika idzi wakapa zvibayiro.

0:12:14.820,0:12:15.840
Unorevei neizvozvo?

0:12:15.840,0:12:18.540
Ungatsanangura zvakaitika here pawakaenda ikoko?

0:12:18.540,0:12:25.420
Pandakaenda ikoko, vaizondiudza kuti  ndi dhiabhorosi ndeichi kana icho.

0:12:25.420,0:12:32.120
Vaizondiudza kuti nditenge mhou huru, ndinyengetera pamusoro payo uye chirwere changu chaizoenda.

0:12:32.120,0:12:34.300
Ini nditori nemimwe yemifananidzo yaizvozvo.

0:12:34.300,0:12:38.140
Kurwara kwangu kwaizodzikira asi apo ini ndaizodzokera, zvaizowedzera

0:12:38.140,0:12:42.140
uye vaizofanira kundipinza muchipatara, vakananga kuchipatara chepfungwa.

0:12:42.140,0:12:46.840
Handai gamuchira mhinduro zvachose.

0:12:46.840,0:12:52.200
Saka, iwe waigara uri anoshandisa zvipatara zve vanorwara ne pfungwa zveku London nekuda kwemaradzo aya?

0:12:52.200,0:12:53.620
Hongu

0:12:53.620,0:12:54.300
Zvakanaka

0:12:54.300,0:12:59.820
Zvino, pakati pezvose izvi, iwe wataura pakutanga kuti ne nyasha dzakakosha dza Mwari wakaenda ku Ghana,

0:12:59.820,0:13:02.800
kwawakatanga kuziviswa nezve SCOAN.

0:13:02.800,0:13:08.820
Dzokorodzai kwatiri madhamu - chii chakaitika pamakawana mukana wekuuya pano, pa SCOAN

0:13:08.820,0:13:11.480
ne kugamuchira Morning Water - Mvura ye Mangwanani.

0:13:11.480,0:13:16.940
Pandakaenda neshamwari yangu, ndakava neropafadzo yekuwana Morning Water

0:13:16.940,0:13:20.360
iyo shamwari yangu yakandikurudzira kuti ndishandise.

0:13:20.360,0:13:21.640
Ndakamuudza kuti ndakanga ndichiri kushandisa zvinhu zvakawanda.

0:13:21.640,0:13:24.400
Akandiudza kuti pano ndipo pekupedzisira kuuya.

0:13:24.400,0:13:26.280
Ndakapindura, "Muzita raJesu!"

0:13:26.280,0:13:31.560
Ndakatanga kuitora pachinzvimbo che mapiritsi.

0:13:31.560,0:13:35.120
Zuva rokutanga apo Morning Water yakashandiswa pandiri mubazi re SCOAN, ku Ghana,

0:13:35.120,0:13:40.320
Ndakaenda kumumba ndokurara semucheche.

0:13:40.320,0:13:43.860
Ndakavata zvakanyanya zvokuti vakazondimutsa kuti nditore kudya kwe mangwanani.

0:13:43.860,0:13:47.900
Ndakanyunyuta kuti ndakanga ndisina kurara kwenguva yakareba, kuti vaifanira kunditendera kurara.

0:13:47.900,0:13:51.080
Saka kare , kurara kwako kwaive kwakaita sei?

0:13:51.080,0:13:54.040
Ndakanga ndiri pamhando mbiri dzakasiyana dzemapiritsi ekukotsirisa.

0:13:54.040,0:13:56.320
Munofanirwa kuziva kuti mamiriro angu aive akanyanya sei.

0:13:56.320,0:14:04.260
Kwete piritsi rimwe chete; 48 mg, ini ndinawo pano, rimwe racho rinenge 36 mg.

0:14:04.260,0:14:13.200
Ndaifanira kutora mapiritsi maviri aya pamwe chete kuti ndikotsire asi kunyange neizvozvo, hope dzaisauya.

0:14:13.200,0:14:18.480
Ndakatombonwa mapiritsi akawandisa pane imwe nguva.

0:14:18.480,0:14:21.720
Ndakagumisira ndiri muchipatara.

0:14:21.720,0:14:26.460
Ndakaiswa pa dhiripi kuti ndiburitse mishonga yose yakanga iri muviri wangu.

0:14:26.460,0:14:30.360
Ndakapotsa ndazviuraya panguva iyoyo.

0:14:30.360,0:14:35.760
Hanzvadzi yedu zvechokwadi yaive ichirarama, nehavi ye muropa yekunwa mapiritsi kuti akwanise kurara.

0:14:35.760,0:14:39.660
Mushure mekugamuchira Morning Water, usiku ihwohwo iwe wakakwanisa kurara zvakanaka

0:14:39.660,0:14:41.980
kekutanga mumakore mazhinji?

0:14:41.980,0:14:43.780
Muupenyu hwangu hwose.

0:14:43.780,0:14:48.380
Ndakarara, ndakati iyi yakanga yakaoma zvikuru.

0:14:48.380,0:14:51.380
Ndinokutendai, Jesu!

0:14:51.380,0:14:56.980
Apo ndakadzokera ku London, ndakawana Morning Water ndikaenda nayo.

0:14:56.980,0:14:59.620
Pandaiva mu London, ndaive ndichiishandisa nguva dzose .

0:14:59.620,0:15:10.100
Ndakaramba kutora mishonga yangu izvo zvaka vhundutsa ana chiremba.

0:15:10.100,0:15:16.880
Asi neropafadzo, rudzi rwana chiremba rwandakanga ndinarwo, ivo vainyatsonzwisisa; vaiva ma Kristu.

0:15:16.880,0:15:19.960
Ivo vakati vainzwisisa kuti Mwari aigona kuporesa.

0:15:19.960,0:15:28.300
Vakandibvunza kuti ndakaenda kupi saka ndakaudza chiremba GP wangu kuti ndaive ku SCOAN ku Nigeria.

0:15:28.300,0:15:31.440
Akati, "Waita zvakanaka, ndinofadzwa nezvawakaita".

0:15:31.440,0:15:34.840
Ms Georgiana Saffa Uchapupu Hwe Morning Water

0:15:34.840,0:15:40.260
Hazvina kukwana. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:15:40.260,0:15:45.400
Aya ndiwo mamiriro ezvinhu zvechokwadi anopfuura simba rezvisikwa.

0:15:45.400,0:15:50.160
Hatisi kuedza, nenzira ipi zvayo, kuyambira kuti vana chiremba havagoni kubatsira vanhu vari mumamiriro ezvinhu akadai,

0:15:50.160,0:15:55.700
asi zviri pachena kuna vose vanzwa nyaya yehanzvadzi yedu kuti zvakanga zvichipfuura simba rekunzwisisa kwevanhu,

0:15:55.700,0:15:59.800
zvakanga zvichidarika simba re vanhu, zvaitoda kupindira kwa Mwari.

0:15:59.800,0:16:04.720
Ndiyo nzira iyo mushure mekugamuchira Morning Water, hanzvadzi yedu yakarega kutora mishonga yose

0:16:04.720,0:16:07.120
yaitemba nayo, kwemakore akawanda kudaro.

0:16:07.120,0:16:11.480
Tirikuona ... chii icho makabata ipapo, madhamu?

0:16:11.480,0:16:13.620
iyi ndiyo mimwe mishonga.

0:16:13.620,0:16:17.360
Ndakanga ndisingadi kuaona zvakare; saka, ndakaabudisa kubva mubhokisi ndokuarasa.

0:16:17.360,0:16:21.460
Ndinongova nezvipaketi zvisina chinhu neni zvino nokuti handidi kuaona zvakare.

0:16:21.460,0:16:23.720
Iwo vavengi vangu.

0:16:23.720,0:16:27.460
Ms Georgiana Saffa Uchapupu Hwe Morning Water

0:16:27.460,0:16:33.760
Hanzvadzi yedu akabata zvimwe zvishomanana zve mhando dzakasiyana siyana dzemapiritsi aakanga achitora kuti aedze

0:16:33.760,0:16:40.080
kuti asunungure mamiriro ake ezvinhu - chirwere chakakomba chepfungwa chaibatanidza ne kutema kwe musoro kwakaipisa,

0:16:40.080,0:16:45.880
pamwe nemamwe matambudziko ezvehutano: hypertension, dambudziko guru remaziso.

0:16:45.880,0:16:49.340
Matambudziko akawanda ehurwere akasiyana siyana akakuvadza upenyu hwehanzvadzi yedu.

0:16:49.340,0:16:52.320
Aive achiita zvakanaka chaizvo mu UK mune basa rine mukurumbira.

0:16:52.320,0:16:56.160
Zvadaro zvinhu zvakaparara, mushure mokunge kutemwa nemusoro kwakanyanya kwakamurova.

0:16:56.160,0:16:59.980
Asi isu tinopa rukudzo kuna Mwari kuti iye akadzorerwa naIshe wedu, Jesu Kristu.

0:16:59.980,0:17:04.700
Madhamu, sekumira kwamakaita pano ikozvino kune kubwinya kwa Mwari, hutano hwenyu huri sei ikozvino?

0:17:04.700,0:17:06.640
Utano hwangu hwakakwana.

0:17:06.640,0:17:09.640
Ndakaderera pahuremu wangu sezvo ndisiri kutora mapiritsi zvakare.

0:17:09.640,0:17:13.580
Ndakanga ndava kusvika pasaizi 22; ikozvino, ini ndiri pasaizi 16.

0:17:13.580,0:17:20.560
Ini ndiri mudzimai mutsva, muzita ra Jesu Kristu we Nazareta na Mwari we mu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:17:20.560,0:17:25.720
Ndinokutendai, Jesu!

0:17:25.720,0:17:31.480
Musoro iwoyo waitema kwazvo uyo wakatanga matambudziko aya epfungwa - munoreva here kuti wakaenda?

0:17:31.480,0:17:32.380
Wakaenda.

0:17:32.380,0:17:38.440
Handina matambudziko, kunyange zvinetso zvekurara; ikozvino, ndinorara semucheche.

0:17:38.440,0:17:40.180
Ndaigona kurara kunyange ndakagara.

0:17:40.180,0:17:43.200
Iye zvino, ndinonwa kofi kuitira kuti ndirege kurara!

0:17:43.200,0:17:44.680
Mungazvibvume here izvozvo?

0:17:44.680,0:17:46.120
Wawu, Ndinokutendai, Jesu Kristu!

0:17:46.120,0:17:51.740
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kamwe zvakare kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:17:51.740,0:17:57.000
Pakupedzisira madhamu, imi mati izvozvi, mushure mokunge Jesu Kristu adzorera utano hwenyu, kune kubwinya kwa Mwari,

0:17:57.000,0:18:04.120
imi makatanga kuyananisana nevamwe vevana venyu, avo vamaive musina kumboona zvachose, kubva pakuberekwa kwavo,

0:18:04.120,0:18:05.840
nekuda kwekukura kwe matambudziko enyu.

0:18:05.840,0:18:10.360
Imi munoreva kuti ikozvino, nenyasha dza Mwari, makakwanisa kuyananiswa uye kusangana nevamwe vavo?

0:18:10.360,0:18:15.700
Hongu, vatatu vevana vangu vakauya kuzondishanyira; ivo vaiva mu Ghana mavhiki matatu apfuura.

0:18:15.700,0:18:21.020
Vakauya kuzondishanyira kekutanga.

0:18:21.020,0:18:27.880
Pavakasvika, vakashamisika vakati, "Mai, machinja! Murikuita sekasikana kadiki."

0:18:27.880,0:18:30.900
Ndakavaudza kuti ini ndave mudzimai mutsva iye zvino.

0:18:30.900,0:18:32.520
Zvinhu zvose zvachinja muupenyu hwangu.

0:18:32.520,0:18:37.400
Vakashamisika kuti ndakanga ndichiita semusikana muduku.

0:18:37.400,0:18:43.700
Kare, taizorwisana uye vaizondisiya vachienda kunogara muhotera.

0:18:43.700,0:18:50.860
Asi ikozvino, tinovata, tinodya, tinofamba famba tinoita zvose pamwe chete.

0:18:50.860,0:18:53.000
Ndakaenda kunotenga zvinhu navo.

0:18:53.000,0:18:58.340
Ini ndinovaperekedza kunhandare ye ndege asi kare ndaiti, "Handiendi, handisi kunzwa zvakanaka".

0:18:58.340,0:19:00.780
Asi ikozvino, ivo vanofara zvikuru.

0:19:00.780,0:19:08.720
Ndakaenda navo kubazi re SCOAN ku Ghana.

0:19:08.720,0:19:11.120
Panguva ino, vanoona pa Youtube.

0:19:11.120,0:19:17.060
Ivo vanofara zvikuru uye vakandikumbira kuti ndivaunzire Morning Water.

0:19:17.060,0:19:19.440
Hareruya! Zviro kwazvo uku kuchinja kukuru.

0:19:19.440,0:19:25.180
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:19:25.180,0:19:26.620
Wawu, Ndinokutendai, Jesu Kristu!

0:19:26.620,0:19:27.960
Tinopa mbiri yese kuna Mwari.

0:19:27.960,0:19:33.500
Hapana mazwi chaiwo okutsanangura zvakaitwa na Jesu Kristu muupenyu hwe hanzvadzi yedu, kunze kwekuti,

0:19:33.500,0:19:34.960
"Ndinokutendai, Jesu".

0:19:34.960,0:19:40.320
Pakupedzisira madhamu, Morning Water iyi yamakabata iye zvino - ndeipi yambiro yenyu ku pasi rose,

0:19:40.320,0:19:45.260
ne kurudziro yenyu kune pasi rose nekuda kwe zvikomborero zvinoshamisa zva Mwari zvamakabata iye zvino

0:19:45.260,0:19:49.340
izvo Mwari akashandisa semudziyo wekudzorera pfungwa, utano,

0:19:49.340,0:19:54.400
mushure memakore akawanda muchitambudzika ne chinetso chakadai?

0:19:54.400,0:20:01.000
Morning Water iyi yakanakisa zvikuru zvokuti handigoni kugara ndisinayo.

0:20:01.000,0:20:06.140
Usatamba nayo, hazvinei ne mamiriro ezvinhu auri kupfuura nemaari, kana chirwere chipi,

0:20:06.140,0:20:08.900
kana dambudziko rawakatarisana naro.

0:20:08.900,0:20:12.080
Tsvaga mhinduro.

0:20:12.080,0:20:14.600
Morning Water ndiyo yakanakisisa - inogona kugadzirisa ...

0:20:14.600,0:20:22.020
Kana ichikwanisa kugadzirisa dambudziko rangu - rakakura zvikuru zvokuti kunyange hurumende ye Britain yaiziva nezvazvo,

0:20:22.020,0:20:24.480
inogona kugadzirisa dambudziko re chero munhu.

0:20:24.480,0:20:26.860
Hapana chinhambwe kuna Jesu.

0:20:26.860,0:20:29.100
Jesu ari kwose kwose pasi rose.

0:20:29.100,0:20:34.800
Morning Water iyi - ishandise zvakanaka kwazvo uye vimba nayo.

0:20:34.800,0:20:40.700
Hanzvadzi dzangu ne vanunu'na vangu - haizoku gumbura, muzita ra Jesu Kristu we Nazareta

0:20:40.700,0:20:43.060
uye Mwari wemu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:20:43.060,0:20:50.760
Ameni! Kamwe zvakare, ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu!

